humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The report indicates that out of 11 assessed lymph nodes, 2 were positive for metastasis (Axillaris 2/11). This corresponds to the N1 stage based on New Rule 12, which states that N1 indicates metastases in 1 to 3 axillary lymph nodes (No/Total).

humanMachineDialogue.text: The patient has 2/11 axillary lymph nodes positive for metastasis, which corresponds to N1 stage. The report does not mention extracapsular invasion, so we cannot consider that in the staging. The substaging information is not provided, so we cannot make a more specific N stage prediction.
